BlackboardClient, Component, PluginBase, PluginStateModel, GenericStateModel
public class AssetDataParamPlugin
extends AssetDataPlugin

Extension of AssetDataPlugin which always uses the ParameterizedDataReader to construct the local entity asset and the Report tasks associated with all the local asset's relationships. Local asset must have ClusterPG and RelationshipPG, Presumption is that the 'other' assets in all the relationships have both Cluster and Relationship PGs. Currently assumes that each Agent has exactly 1 local asset.

See Also:
AssetDataParamReader
